OL,3,CBig change in London youth policing
OL,4,C'catastrophic' warns principal
OL,6,FA major change to the way youth
OL,7,Fpolicing is carried out across London
OL,8,Fwas described by a school principal as
OL,9,F"catastrophic" which left her feeling
OL,10,F"crushed".
OL,12,FJessica West from Ark Walworth Academy
OL,13,Fcriticised the decision to switch
OL,14,Fofficers away from their highly
OL,15,Fvisible role in schools and into
OL,16,Fcommunity policing.
OL,18,FThe change affects hundreds of roles
OL,19,Fand means officers will focus more on
OL,20,Fcommunity policing and on children as
OL,21,Fthey travel to and from school.
