OL,3,CBig change in London youth policing
OL,4,C'catastrophic' warns principal
OL,6,FSpeaking to the London Assembly,
OL,7,FJessica West said: "I think this is
OL,8,Fthe single most catastrophic decision
OL,9,Fin keeping children safe in the last
OL,10,F10 years of my professional experience.
OL,12,F"I am crushed by it personally.
OL,14,F"(I'm) at a loss to explain how it's
OL,15,Fhappened".
OL,17,FThe Met says police will ensure safety
OL,18,Fon school commute routes which are
OL,19,Fseen as higher-risk areas and officers
OL,20,Fwill retain strong relationships with
OL,21,Fschools.
