OL,3,CBig change in London youth policing
OL,4,C'catastrophic' warns principal
OL,6,FWhen Quamari Serunkuma-Barnes was
OL,7,Fmurdered in 2017 he had only just
OL,8,Fstepped outside his school gates.
OL,10,FThe 15-year-old was chased by a fellow
OL,11,Fpupil the same age who stabbed him
OL,12,Fthree times.
OL,14,FAt the time the school had a Safer
OL,15,FSchools Officer but this year that
OL,16,Frole has been axed.
OL,18,FQuamari's mother said the officer may
OL,19,Fnot have prevented her son's death,
OL,20,Fbut people should have been consulted.
